{"id":17409,"date":"2024-02-16T17:48:54","date_gmt":"2020-12-16T12:18:54","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=17409"},"modified":"2022-04-08T12:03:52","modified_gmt":"2022-04-08T06:33:52","slug":"drawing-room-decoration-ideas","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/drawing-room-interiors\/drawing-room-decoration-ideas\/","title":{"rendered":"Seven Effective Drawing Room Decoration Ideas"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p><em>Creative ways to create a welcoming drawing room in your home<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>When designing homes, the spaces given a great deal of thought include the living or drawing rooms, and rightfully so! Typically, these are the spaces where you entertain friends and relatives on special occasions and unwind with the family. Most importantly, a drawing room is one of the first things that anyone who comes over notices in your home. It is, therefore, crucial to tastefully design the drawing room to make the right first impression of your style and taste.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Traditionally, drawing rooms are entertainment rooms separate from the living room in a house. Modern homes today may not come with a separate room just for entertaining guests. But your living\/drawing room can definitely be designed and decorated in a manner that sets a comfortable vibe for when guests are over at your place. These seven drawing room decoration ideas are entirely doable in a modern home setting.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Clean Spaces<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This drawing room looks bright and welcoming. The white ceiling and walls make the space look clean and fresh. Big windows on the right make it an open living space, which when combined with the warm colour tones of the curtains gives the place a breezy look. The drawing room decoration, including the colour scheme, the lamp, the rug and the wall decor, are all minimal and in harmony with each other, delivering on the vibe that the room demands.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/16174153\/minimal-drawing-room-decoration.jpg\" alt=\"Minimal drawing room decoration with a colour scheme, the rug and the wall artsy looks bright and welcoming.\" class=\"wp-image-17416\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/16174153\/minimal-drawing-room-decoration.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/16174153\/minimal-drawing-room-decoration-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/16174153\/minimal-drawing-room-decoration-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/16174153\/minimal-drawing-room-decoration-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Minimal drawing room design can simply be a play of colours and textures<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Do you want a living room that is lively and livable\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/02171514\/living-room-lively-livable.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Drawing Room Decoration For Compact Spaces<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>When your living room doubles up as the drawing room (which is the case with most modern homes, big or small), the right decor can help give the room its own personality like the one in question. The minimal room has a fuss-free, yet comfortable, seating arrangement, complete with a warm rug on the floor for optimum interior decoration of drawing room. The pictures and lamp add to the cosy setting. Flowers and potted plants add a bit of charm and a pop of colour to space.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/16174136\/compact-small-room-drawing-room-decoration-ideas.jpg\" alt=\"Compact small drawing room decoration with photos, lamp, flowers and potted plants add a bit of charm to space.\" class=\"wp-image-17413\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/16174136\/compact-small-room-drawing-room-decoration-ideas.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/16174136\/compact-small-room-drawing-room-decoration-ideas-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/16174136\/compact-small-room-drawing-room-decoration-ideas-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/16174136\/compact-small-room-drawing-room-decoration-ideas-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Small drawings rooms can look inviting with thoughtful design<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Artsy Drawing Room Decor<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The room shows the artistic nature of the homeowner. The first thing that draws your attention is an ornate mirror piece on the right wall. The room has a false ceiling which has enabled the owner to be creative with overhead lighting. The homey sofa and coffee table are the perfect set-up for having loved ones over. The partition cleverly divides the entertaining area from the rest of the room, while still keeping the space open. This room is proof that you can be practical and artistically whimsy at the same time with the design and decor.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/16174124\/artsy-drawing-room-wall-decoration.jpg\" alt=\"Partitioned drawing room decorated with an ornate mirror piece, false ceiling and sofa is how to decorate a drawing-room.\" class=\"wp-image-17411\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/16174124\/artsy-drawing-room-wall-decoration.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/16174124\/artsy-drawing-room-wall-decoration-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/16174124\/artsy-drawing-room-wall-decoration-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/16174124\/artsy-drawing-room-wall-decoration-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Bold decor makes for an artistic drawing room<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Modern Monochrome<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The colour palette does all the work for this drawing room. If you are wondering how to decorate drawing rooms efficiently and with minimal intervention, here is your inspiration. The dark colours are balanced with white decor and fabrics to ensure the room doesn\u2019t feel dark and unwelcoming. Pops of colour are added with fresh flowers, greens and bright art and decor on the shelves. The additional seating on the floor immensely helps in setting the right tone for the drawing room.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/16174159\/monochrome-interior-decoration-in-drawing-dining-room.jpg\" alt=\"Modern drawing room decoration with pops of colour added with fresh flowers, greens and bright art looks inviting.\" class=\"wp-image-17417\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/16174159\/monochrome-interior-decoration-in-drawing-dining-room.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/16174159\/monochrome-interior-decoration-in-drawing-dining-room-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/16174159\/monochrome-interior-decoration-in-drawing-dining-room-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/16174159\/monochrome-interior-decoration-in-drawing-dining-room-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Dark colours for the drawing room can make it look inviting<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Love this design? Make it your own\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/02171045\/love-this-living-room-design.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Colour Play<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>\u201cMagnanimity\u201d is the word for this room. Though the drawing room is pretty formal and sophisticated, the light colours deliver a softer touch to the space. The decorative items for drawing room do the trick and the chic hanging lamp adds a classy touch to the decor. The walls are minimally decorated to let the largeness of the space do most of the talking.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/16174130\/colour-play-drawing-room-decoration-images.jpg\" alt=\"Drawing room wall decoration in a minimal way with the chic hanging lamp and light colours wall adds a softer touch.\" class=\"wp-image-17412\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/16174130\/colour-play-drawing-room-decoration-images.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/16174130\/colour-play-drawing-room-decoration-images-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/16174130\/colour-play-drawing-room-decoration-images-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/16174130\/colour-play-drawing-room-decoration-images-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Sophisticated designs retain the grandeur of large drawing rooms<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Drawing Room Decoration For An Urbane Apartment<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This urbane space is extremely elegant in its decor. The light and bright colours and the natural greens make the small drawing room look spacious. The stylish decor pieces are in sync with each other &#8212; the hanging lamps, the cute swing shelf, the hampers and the wall frames make the drawing room look extremely charming.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/16174141\/drawing-room-decoration-for-urbane-apartment.jpg\" alt=\"Hanging lamps, the cute swing shelf, and the wall frames bring charming to space is the small drawing room decoration ideas.\" class=\"wp-image-17414\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/16174141\/drawing-room-decoration-for-urbane-apartment.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/16174141\/drawing-room-decoration-for-urbane-apartment-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/16174141\/drawing-room-decoration-for-urbane-apartment-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/16174141\/drawing-room-decoration-for-urbane-apartment-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Modern drawing rooms call for modern designs<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Drawing Room Decoration Without Sofas<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The cane furniture used in this space has a distinct quality of transforming the whole room. The unique aspect of this room is that different and quirky seating options have been incorporated instead of a sofa, which would have been limiting in a space like this. Plants go with the natural theme of the room. The painting on the wall adds a modern appeal.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/16174204\/simple-drawing-room-decoration-with-sofas.jpg\" alt=\"Simple drawing room decoration with different seating options, indoor plants and painting on the wall adds a modern appeal.\" class=\"wp-image-17418\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/16174204\/simple-drawing-room-decoration-with-sofas.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/16174204\/simple-drawing-room-decoration-with-sofas-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/16174204\/simple-drawing-room-decoration-with-sofas-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/16174204\/simple-drawing-room-decoration-with-sofas-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Look for alternative seating options in smaller drawing rooms<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>You can get really creative with drawing room decor, no matter the size of the space. Get in touch with us at <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/\">Design Cafe<\/a> for end-to-end design and decor solutions for your home.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Also Read:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/drawing-room-interiors\/latest-drawing-room-design-ideas\/\">Latest Drawing Room Design Ideas<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/drawing-room-interiors\/wall-design-ideas\/\">Wall Design Ideas<\/a><\/li><\/ul>\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Elevate Your Home's Interior Design<\/h3>\n  \n \n     <p class=\"text-center text-dark mt-0\"> B